webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) "Included in a series with Fotonr. 5419 with the different postcards of the Gothenburg Museum of Natural History over the years. : Bark coral from the Gulf of Agami in japan, which was returned to the Museum of Natural History in Gothenburg by Sixten Bock. Printed on the back: "The Museum of Natural History, Gothenburg 11, Sweden... 19...Dear sir, We have the great experience of your kindness to send us...
